ion type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11036">Burckhard, Max</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1905_01">Burckhard an Schnitzler, undatiert</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1907-01-26_01">Burckhard an Schnitzler, 26. 1. 1907</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
